Body:
Description: Hello,

Previously, just based on old reports, it looks like we were able to find some PII using the DLP scans in StealthAUDIT. As of now, though, when we run them, it is returning no data even though we know there are files on the servers that have PII. We haven't been able to figure out why it's not returning any data and would like some assistance, thanks!
What We've Learned Updated: Sensitive Data was not installed
Next Steps Updated: I am waiting for an update from the customer before I can close this ticket.
